# Amazon Nitro CLI resource allocation configuration


config NITRO_CLI_RESOURCE_ALLOCATOR
	tristate "Nitro CLI resource allocation support"
	---help---
	  This driver supports memory allocation / free and
          cpu mapping / unmapping for Nitro CLI.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here.
	  The module will be called nitro_cli_resource_allocator.
